| eventBus
| no
| object
| EventBus options

| eventPoolSize
| no
| integer
| Configure event pool size.  Default: *2*.

| orderedBlockingHandlers
| no
| boolean
| Configure, whether blocking handlers for mutating requests should be ordered.  Default: *true*.

